claim.claim-text:
1. A liquid oxygen tank apparatus comprising: 
a) a tank body having a wall with inner and outer surfaces, the inner surface defining a hollow interior for containing liquid oxygen; 
b) the tank wall comprising a composite construction that includes a fiber reinforced halogenated resin.

21. A launch vehicle comprising: 
a) an air frame; 
b) an engine; 
c) liquid oxygen for fueling the engine; 
d) a tank for containing said liquid oxygen, the tank comprising: 
i) a tank body having a wall with inner and outer surfaces, the inner surface defining a hollow interior for containing liquid oxygen; 
ii) the tank wall comprising a composite construction that includes a fiber reinforced halogenated resin.
